      "text": "n =  17\n\n\n00000.... 010001\n\nn >> 1  ===> 000000...001000 ---> 8\n\nn >> 2 ===> 00000.000100 -> 4\n\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
